  "texts": [
    "This method assessed and compared the effectiveness of each version of Effi-cientNet on a multiclass classification problem with unequal class representations.",
    "Efficient-Net-B4 and B5 Models with an intermediate level of complexity provide the best performance results.",
    "Alwakid et al.",
    "[28] created the DL method to extract prominent features from the infected area of skin.",
    "To improve the image's quality at first, ESRGAN was employed."
